author: Roborider_in_the_sky
title: Preety cool Rahi
review:
The Barakki Deepsea patrol was the first playset of 07' that I got.
Pros
Heads are correct colors
Black tentacales
White visorak fangs
Bubble thigy
Glowing tentecales on the jelly fish
Squid lancers is made of stiffer plastic
4  Bionicle mini figs
Most of set is vecihle

Cons 
New white cone pieces
Vahki staff legs
Repeted wepons
no shooting method for spheres

Not a bad set, And better than the other $30 playsets of former years.
